# Anthropic API Key
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
# 1. Sign up or log in to your Anthropic account
# 2. Go to API Keys section
# 3. Create a new API key
# 4. Copy the key (it starts with 'sk-ant-api03-')
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace 'your_api_key_here' with your actual Anthropic API key
# 3. Never commit .env.local to git (it's already in .gitignore)

# For Vercel deployment:
# Add the ANTHROPIC_API_KEY as an environment variable in your Vercel project settings
